<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width">
    <title>Rozzo</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Raleway&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="main.css">

</head>

<body>

    <div class="header">
        <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row;
  align-items: center;">


            <img src="logo.svg" style="filter: invert(1); width: 20vw;">

            <h1>
                Allergy Detection
            </h1>
        </div>

        <a href="/login">
            Login
        </a>

    </div>

    <div class="body">


        <p style="margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;">
            Rozzo Allergen Detection is a website that lets you scan ingredients
			from packaged goods and tells you whether you are allergic to anything
			in it. This website dedicated to the memory of Caroline Rozzo.	
        </p>

        <h2>Sign Up!</h2>

        <form class="sign-up-form " method = POST action = 'createAccount'>

            <input type="text" id="username" placeholder="Username">

            <input type="password" id="password" placeholder="Password">

            <input type="password" id="confirmPassword" placeholder="Retype Password">

            <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; flex-wrap: nowrap;">
                <textarea id="weakness" placeholder="What can't you eat?"></textarea>
            </div>

            <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items:center ">



                <select>
                    <option value="placeholder">Dairy</option>
                    <option value="placeholder">Hallal</option>
                    <option value="placeholder">Kosher</option>
                    <option value="placeholder">Nuts</option>
                    <option value="placeholder">Shellfish</option>
                    <option value="placeholder">Vegan</option>


                </select>

                <button type="button" style="font-size: 15px;">Add Preset</button>


            </div>

            <button  type="submit">Chow Down!</button>


        </form>



    </div>

    <div>

        <a href="/profile">Profile</a>
        <a href="/upload">Upload</a>


    </div>
</body>

</html>